###########################################################################
#  figure_with_caption - a @Figure floating environment with an @Caption #
#  containing arbitrary text, exercising the formal caption pathway      #
#  (not just hand-typed "Figure 1." labels as in fig_numbering.lt).      #
###########################################################################

@SysInclude { diag }
@SysInclude { doc }
@Doc @Text @Begin
@PP
The figure below is wrapped in a real @Code "@Figure" float with a
formal @Code "@Caption".

@Figure
   @Caption { A small diagram with two connected nodes. }
@Begin
@CentredDisplay @Diag {
A:: @Circle { a } ||2c B:: @Circle { b }
// @Link from { A } to { B } arrow { yes }
}
@End @Figure

@PP
Text continues after the caption.
@End @Text
